nodes.text: A human man resided on Five Points station. When Jyn Erso was 18 years old and staying there, the man solicited her sexually. She rejected his advances, and in response he called Jyn a "coldhearted Kath".
Jyn pickpocketed the man while he was making overtures to her. She gave the credits she stole from him to a Huloon beggar on the station.
